data.description: Looking to get away from the big city life, either full time or just occasionally? This home is located on the backside of Bear Valley Springs, a gated mountain community not far from the City of Tehachapi. The home has amazing views of Arvin, Bakersfield and the San Joaquin Valley and sits on almost 16 acres. The home is over 2500SF with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms in a split wing design. With over 70 solar panels and the seller paying off the solar contract, you won't have to worry about paying another electricity bill again!  The enormous kitchen has a brand new double oven and dishwasher, gas and electric cooktops, microwave oven and even a prep sink on the supersized island. The large family room has vaulted tongue and groove ceilings, a newer wood burning stove, built in entertainment center with wet bar, wine fridge and surround sound speakers. The formal dining room can be used as a den with plenty of room for a dining table in the kitchen area. The master bedroom has 2 patios off of it, with one of them being enclosed, perfect for a spa or home gym area. The master bathroom has a giant walk in shower as well as a jet tub, dual sinks and a walk in closet. The oversized laundry room has plenty of storage, a pantry area and brand new laminate flooring, along with a washer and dryer that stay with the property. The garage has 2 oversized stalls and one extra tall stall that allows you to park your lifted truck or tractor inside. There are also 2 workshop/bonus rooms behind the garage, giving you plenty of room to have your man cave or craft room. The home has a covered wrap around front porch to go along with the other 3 patio areas, room for horses, a garden area and you can enjoy the elk, deer and other wildlife without leaving your property. The lot next door at 28321 Deertrail is also available for $19k and if purchased, that would give you over 18 acres! Come see this mountain top getaway soon!
